This map is a remake of fun_assault_alpha2. The concept of the game is similar to backalley_run_v2 (look it up, not my map) and its basically t's with scoutz on one located area. The cts run and scavage for weapons and kill the t's. But the cts have to reach to the t's building to kill them. Oh by the way, there are explosives!
